modName: Arfentur - A male nord lvl 26 NO CHEATS
summary: This is my own savegame. I called him Arfentur, and he\'s a male nord specialist in one-handed and archery.
descriptionHtml:
Arfentur, a hard warrior specialist in one-handed and archery. He\'s level 26 almost 27.

- Main story completed.
- Companions completed.
- Breezehome bought and fully equiped.
- Proudspire Manor bought and fully equiped.
- One-handed about lvl 70.
- Archery about lvl 60.
- The other skills are about lvl 20 - 50.
- Married with Aela The Huntress (she is in Jorrvaskr).
- About 10000 gold.
- Some weapons and armor enchanted.
- About 10 or 20 spells.

Mods I use (in this save game):

- Final Fantasy 7 Crisis Core Buster Sword (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2699)
- Olivia Wilde (as Lydia) (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6459)
- Phallus Arrows (LOL) (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3773)
- Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces - New hairstyles (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488)
- Athletic Nude Women - CBBE (http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/563)

Instalation:

Put the .ess and .ess.bak (both) files in /Documents (or My Documents)/My Games/Skyrim/Saves

If anything comes up let me know it. If you have a problem, send me a message.
